WEBVTT

00:01:56.700 --> 00:01:58.400
Can everyone stop playing on their phones?

00:01:58.400 --> 00:01:59.760
Hurry up and share your ideas.

00:02:00.859 --> 00:02:02.340
There's less than a week left.

00:02:02.500 --> 00:02:03.680
In such a short time,

00:02:04.060 --> 00:02:05.959
I feel like our internship assignment...

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:08.039
...won't really break new ground.

00:02:08.060 --> 00:02:08.840
Even if you had more time,

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:10.500
could you come up with anything new?

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:12.159
Then we could...

00:02:12.979 --> 00:02:14.319
...still not come up with anything new.

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:15.180
That's true.

00:02:15.699 --> 00:02:16.879
Anyway, if you ask me,

00:02:17.099 --> 00:02:18.580
as long as we don't have to write a paper.

00:02:18.900 --> 00:02:20.300
Whoever wants to write it can write it.

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:22.099
I just don't want to make trouble for myself.

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:23.280
How about...

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:24.900
...we don't write it individually?

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:27.180
Let's do a co-created paper.

00:02:27.439 --> 00:02:28.500
To visually demonstrate...

00:02:28.539 --> 00:02:30.860
...our understanding and research of the silver industry.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:31.979
Great!

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:33.539
You guys write it together.

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:35.240
Just put my name on it at the end.

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:36.240
Good idea.

00:02:36.300 --> 00:02:37.979
You wish.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:40.099
I have a proposal.

00:02:40.639 --> 00:02:42.419
We can take this internship period...

00:02:42.419 --> 00:02:44.139
...and all the wonderful stories we experienced...

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:45.439
...and turn them into a one-act play.

00:02:45.780 --> 00:02:46.360
This way,

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:47.240
it has content,

00:02:47.319 --> 00:02:48.099
it has a perspective,

00:02:48.259 --> 00:02:49.259
and it's still original.

00:02:50.699 --> 00:02:51.960
That idea is really...

00:02:51.979 --> 00:02:52.939
...not that great.

00:02:53.819 --> 00:02:55.319
Look, there's less than a week left.

00:02:55.900 --> 00:02:57.159
We have to write the script,

00:02:57.340 --> 00:02:58.479
prepare costumes,

00:02:58.539 --> 00:02:59.379
and rehearse.

00:02:59.379 --> 00:03:00.900
We definitely won't make it in time.

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:02.300
Besides,

00:03:02.599 --> 00:03:04.000
who would play who?

00:03:04.699 --> 00:03:05.780
Yingzi and I...

00:03:05.979 --> 00:03:07.460
...will play Ms. Liu and Auntie Cai.

00:03:07.699 --> 00:03:08.780
Yusheng, Wang Song...

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:10.139
...Li Zong, Professor Fan.

00:03:10.300 --> 00:03:12.199
You play Grandpa Gou'er.

00:03:12.259 --> 00:03:13.280
Wait, that confused old man?

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:14.419
Why should I play him?

00:03:14.500 --> 00:03:15.979
Your vibes are quite similar.

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:18.099
Is Li Zong reliable?

00:03:18.379 --> 00:03:19.620
And Professor Fan isn't exactly...

00:03:19.620 --> 00:03:20.840
...a rule-abiding old man either.

00:03:21.460 --> 00:03:21.939
Me?

00:03:22.300 --> 00:03:23.379
What do I play?

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:24.719
You...

00:03:25.599 --> 00:03:27.400
...can only play Granny Jin.

00:03:27.500 --> 00:03:29.759
The age gap is pretty big,

00:03:29.819 --> 00:03:31.259
but just try your best...

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:32.900
...to embody the character.

00:03:34.020 --> 00:03:35.199
I can't act.

00:03:35.259 --> 00:03:36.360
I can't act either.

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:38.500
The key is that time doesn't allow it.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:40.319
Then what do we do?

00:03:40.599 --> 00:03:41.280
We can't just...

00:03:41.319 --> 00:03:43.199
...shoot a short video for our assignment?

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.199
No...

00:03:46.199 --> 00:03:48.340
If not, just pretend I didn't say anything.

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:49.539
Xiaoxin!

00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:51.460
That idea is solid!

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.300
Let's do that.

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:53.599
Zhu Zhu.

00:03:54.039 --> 00:03:54.520
Zhu Zhu!

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:56.319
Stop playing. Notify the elders first.

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:57.900
Let them prepare thoroughly.

00:03:58.000 --> 00:03:58.639
Just say...

00:03:58.840 --> 00:03:59.879
...we start filming in half an hour.

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:00.340
Okay.

00:04:01.860 --> 00:04:02.280
Wait, no.

00:04:02.460 --> 00:04:02.979
Hold on a second.

00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:04.580
Half an hour?

00:04:05.039 --> 00:04:06.219
Is that enough time to prepare?

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:06.780
Well...

00:04:09.800 --> 00:04:10.639
That works

00:04:13.199 --> 00:04:13.740
Ready

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:15.319
Action

00:04:16.439 --> 00:04:17.519
Can't see my lower body, right?

00:04:19.579 --> 00:04:20.199
Li Zong

00:04:20.379 --> 00:04:21.660
Didn't I just tell you?

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:22.660
You can't see it

00:04:22.779 --> 00:04:23.699
Just relax

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:25.019
Then I'm relieved

00:04:27.379 --> 00:04:28.019
Ready

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:29.980
Action

00:04:30.439 --> 00:04:32.120
The key is you didn't tell me earlier

00:04:32.300 --> 00:04:33.220
Otherwise

00:04:33.300 --> 00:04:34.920
I would have prepared a bit more

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.680
It's okay

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:38.240
Again

00:04:38.300 --> 00:04:39.740
No need to be nervous, Li Zong

00:04:39.819 --> 00:04:40.399
Nervous

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.439
What a joke

00:04:41.959 --> 00:04:43.500
When have I, Li Jianguo, ever been nervous?

00:04:43.500 --> 00:04:45.180
What big scenes haven't I seen?

00:04:45.300 --> 00:04:45.519
Right

00:04:45.519 --> 00:04:46.500
Back then, the TV station

00:04:46.579 --> 00:04:48.019
filmed me with such huge cameras

00:04:48.939 --> 00:04:50.540
Let alone this tiny phone

00:04:50.699 --> 00:04:51.360
Right

00:04:51.420 --> 00:04:52.279
Just like back then

00:04:52.279 --> 00:04:53.879
when you were interviewed on TV

00:04:53.879 --> 00:04:55.339
Just say whatever you want to say

00:04:55.399 --> 00:04:55.879
Right

00:04:56.100 --> 00:04:57.079
Just like back then

00:04:57.379 --> 00:04:57.639
Right

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:58.819
You should have said so earlier

00:04:59.259 --> 00:05:00.160
That would have saved so much trouble

00:05:00.779 --> 00:05:01.319
Okay

00:05:01.319 --> 00:05:01.680
Come on

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:03.759
Ready

00:05:03.980 --> 00:05:05.079
Action

00:05:05.839 --> 00:05:07.579
Dear viewers in front of your TVs

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:08.680
Hello, everyone

00:05:09.399 --> 00:05:11.779
I am the Deputy General Manager of Xin Chao Kai Group

00:05:11.839 --> 00:05:12.600
Li Jianguo

00:05:15.699 --> 00:05:17.019
Old Li, that guy

00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:19.000
is just too opinionated

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:21.120
Arrogant and conceited

00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:23.399
Always thinks he's so amazing

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:24.579
At every turn

00:05:24.740 --> 00:05:25.779
he talks about that bit of

00:05:25.819 --> 00:05:27.500
glorious history, hard to tell if true or false

00:05:27.879 --> 00:05:30.500
That was a life-or-death lawsuit

00:05:31.579 --> 00:05:32.540
The legal representative at the time

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:35.160
was President Jia, current President Ma's father-in-law

00:05:35.939 --> 00:05:37.699
forgot to bring the materials

00:05:38.379 --> 00:05:39.759
He was so anxious!

00:05:40.060 --> 00:05:41.620
He broke down right then

00:05:41.939 --> 00:05:43.439
The other directors of the company

00:05:43.519 --> 00:05:45.000
all shrank back one by one

00:05:45.500 --> 00:05:46.160
They even said

00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:47.920
"Why don't we just settle with them?"

00:05:48.620 --> 00:05:49.699
But I

00:05:50.180 --> 00:05:51.259
as the Deputy General Manager

00:05:51.519 --> 00:05:52.839
stepped forward

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:54.040
It was truly

00:05:54.579 --> 00:05:56.819
Mount Tai crumbling before me without flinching

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:59.660
a tsunami behind me without gasping

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:00.519
At that moment, I

00:06:00.579 --> 00:06:01.519
slammed the table

00:06:06.740 --> 00:06:08.339
My Iron Palm is still here

00:06:08.759 --> 00:06:10.379
The power hasn't faded a bit

00:06:11.879 --> 00:06:12.540
Continue

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:13.620
Grandpa, please continue

00:06:13.959 --> 00:06:14.899
No internal injuries, right?

00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:17.000
What do you mean internal injuries?

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.319
You're bragging more and more now

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:19.339
You even believe it yourself

00:06:21.620 --> 00:06:22.220
Students

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.879
I strongly request to get this person out

00:06:25.079 --> 00:06:26.279
It's awkward with him here

00:06:26.339 --> 00:06:26.779
No

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:28.500
Why should I leave?

00:06:28.500 --> 00:06:29.839
This is my room!

00:06:30.100 --> 00:06:31.060
Fine, from now on

00:06:31.060 --> 00:06:32.319
I won't speak, okay?

00:06:32.319 --> 00:06:33.060
That won't work either

00:06:33.480 --> 00:06:34.600
I can't speak with him here

00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:36.420
You haven't said enough already?

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:38.560
You've used up all the phone's memory talking

00:06:38.980 --> 00:06:39.720
Are you leaving or not?

00:06:40.079 --> 00:06:41.699
If you don't leave, I'll give you an Air Palm

00:06:45.399 --> 00:06:46.160
Don't worry, you guys

00:06:46.459 --> 00:06:47.699
I'm definitely different from him

00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:49.459
That's great

00:06:50.259 --> 00:06:52.240
What I have to say is backed by evidence

00:07:02.220 --> 00:07:02.920
This right here...

00:07:03.339 --> 00:07:05.180
was the first award I won in my life.

00:07:06.339 --> 00:07:07.079
Have you started filming?

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:08.879
I'm filming.

00:07:08.879 --> 00:07:09.540
Then why don't you...

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:10.180
get a little closer?

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:10.920
Give it a close-up.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:11.639
You got it.

00:07:13.100 --> 00:07:14.000
That won't do.

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:15.639
This angle blocks the light.

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:17.139
How about this side?

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.259
This side is backlit.

00:07:18.660 --> 00:07:19.519
This angle doesn't work either.

00:07:19.519 --> 00:07:19.879
No good.

00:07:19.879 --> 00:07:20.180
Then...

00:07:20.180 --> 00:07:20.600
here...

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:21.000
this angle.

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:21.540
Don't...

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:22.699
try not to block the light.

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:25.100
This...

00:07:25.420 --> 00:07:26.300
was when I graduated from university...

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:27.639
my first year of work.

00:07:27.959 --> 00:07:29.100
I stayed on at the school back then.

00:07:30.180 --> 00:07:31.860
Why do you keep filming the certificate?

00:07:32.040 --> 00:07:33.040
Right now you should...

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:33.899
film me.

00:07:33.959 --> 00:07:35.519
Film a frontal close-up of me.

00:07:37.399 --> 00:07:39.180
We'd need a multi-camera setup for that.

00:07:39.279 --> 00:07:40.639
Even that wouldn't be enough for you.

00:07:41.259 --> 00:07:42.420
My friends...

00:07:43.100 --> 00:07:45.459
Old Li, you guys filmed so many shots...

00:07:45.660 --> 00:07:47.379
you used up all the phone memory.

00:07:47.439 --> 00:07:48.240
Why is it that when it's my turn

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:49.720
to film a few awards and certificates,

00:07:49.819 --> 00:07:50.779
you get annoyed?

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.879
I finally have this rare opportunity

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:56.139
to showcase my life's academic achievements.

00:07:56.139 --> 00:07:56.560
Film.

00:07:57.180 --> 00:07:57.680
Film.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:58.560
Professor Fan,

00:07:58.759 --> 00:07:59.500
he was wrong.

00:07:59.620 --> 00:08:00.519
We were wrong. Keep filming.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:05.839
Hey.

00:08:06.079 --> 00:08:07.579
Xiaoxin, why don't you go say it?

00:08:07.579 --> 00:08:08.699
You're close with Auntie Cai.

00:08:08.939 --> 00:08:10.600
With that mouth of hers...

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:12.540
Me, setting three ground rules with her?

00:08:12.839 --> 00:08:13.439
No way.

00:08:13.439 --> 00:08:14.420
I can't out-talk her.

00:08:14.420 --> 00:08:14.779
You.

00:08:16.199 --> 00:08:16.879
Me?

00:08:17.079 --> 00:08:17.839
I can't do it either.

00:08:18.139 --> 00:08:19.279
Don't bully me just because I'm simple.

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:21.019
Well...

00:08:22.980 --> 00:08:24.160
What's the big deal?

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:24.920
I'll do it.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:26.839
Watch this.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.879
When it counts, we can rely on Keke.

00:08:28.959 --> 00:08:29.680
Come on, let's go in.

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:31.680
Wait.

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:33.419
What was the first rule again?

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:34.299
One.

00:08:34.659 --> 00:08:36.019
No reminiscing about the past.

00:08:36.139 --> 00:08:36.500
Two.

00:08:36.600 --> 00:08:37.879
No blowing your own horn.

00:08:37.980 --> 00:08:38.399
Three.

00:08:38.580 --> 00:08:40.639
No forcing lectures on people...

00:08:40.639 --> 00:08:42.860
...or assigning 3,000-word essays.

00:08:44.980 --> 00:08:46.000
Auntie Cai.

00:08:46.759 --> 00:08:47.860
You scared me!

00:08:48.039 --> 00:08:49.039
You're all here.

00:08:49.580 --> 00:08:50.440
Um...

00:08:50.539 --> 00:08:52.220
Have the two old gentlemen finished filming?

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:54.100
Alright then.

00:08:54.580 --> 00:08:56.019
You guys go inside and wait for me.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:57.139
I'm going to the convenience store...

00:08:57.220 --> 00:08:58.480
...to wash some drinks for you.

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:00.120
To buy some drinks.

00:09:00.679 --> 00:09:01.919
The fruit is already washed.

00:09:01.940 --> 00:09:02.940
It's on the bable.

00:09:02.940 --> 00:09:03.399
Table.

00:09:03.500 --> 00:09:03.940
What?

00:09:04.100 --> 00:09:05.279
It's on the table.

00:09:05.379 --> 00:09:06.840
Help yourselves.

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:08.220
Auntie Cai.

00:09:08.299 --> 00:09:09.659
With that famous mouth of yours...

00:09:09.659 --> 00:09:11.100
...how did you get so tongue-tied today?

00:09:11.879 --> 00:09:12.700
In all my life...

00:09:12.759 --> 00:09:13.899
...it's my first time on TV.

00:09:13.980 --> 00:09:15.059
I'm a bit vous-ner.

00:09:15.620 --> 00:09:17.320
Nervous.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:20.340
Go on in.

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:21.080
Wait there.

00:09:24.299 --> 00:09:26.879
When do I announce the three ground rules?

00:09:27.299 --> 00:09:28.840
I don't think we need them anymore.

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:29.679
Auntie Cai.

00:09:30.659 --> 00:09:31.600
Don't be nervous.

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:32.600
Don't take it too seriously.

00:09:32.679 --> 00:09:34.879
Just like when we take selfies for fun.

00:09:35.019 --> 00:09:35.399
Okay.

00:09:36.899 --> 00:09:37.500
Auntie Cai.

00:09:37.879 --> 00:09:39.639
Let's try shooting a take first.

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:40.679
Okay.

00:09:41.820 --> 00:09:43.139
Alright, I'm starting.

00:09:45.379 --> 00:09:46.279
You can try...

00:09:46.419 --> 00:09:47.320
...doing a self-introduction.

00:09:47.940 --> 00:09:48.360
Okay.

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:52.820
My surname is...

00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:55.039
What is my surname?

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:56.379
Cai.

00:09:56.480 --> 00:09:57.820
Surname Cai. Cai.

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:00.940
My surname is Cai.

00:10:03.539 --> 00:10:04.159
Darn it.

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:06.399
Cai Xiaoying.

00:10:07.279 --> 00:10:08.580
How old are you this year?

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.259
Born in '59.

00:10:11.039 --> 00:10:11.779
Please tell us...

00:10:11.980 --> 00:10:13.840
...about any interesting things you've experienced.

00:10:14.279 --> 00:10:16.240
I haven't experienced anything interesting.

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:17.919
Auntie Cai...

00:10:18.019 --> 00:10:19.240
You can talk about...

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:21.039
...the achievements you've made.

00:10:22.919 --> 00:10:24.480
I haven't made any achievements.

00:10:26.379 --> 00:10:27.120
Do you...

00:10:27.539 --> 00:10:29.519
...have anything you want to say to everyone?

00:10:32.220 --> 00:10:33.980
I have nothing to say to everyone, you guys.

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:38.240
I really didn't expect this.

00:10:38.340 --> 00:10:39.000
Usually...

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:41.039
...the so articulate Auntie Cai...

00:10:41.100 --> 00:10:43.440
...is like this in front of a camera.

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.860
Yangliu Xincheng...

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.639
...Retirement Community.

00:10:49.700 --> 00:10:51.139
Senior Citizens' Pact.

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:52.740
Love the motherland.

00:10:52.879 --> 00:10:53.360
Love...

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:54.860
I think maybe we should put on a skit...

00:10:54.860 --> 00:10:56.539
...and just hand that in as our assignment.

00:10:56.620 --> 00:10:57.500
If all else fails...

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:59.799
I'll stick on a mustache and play Grandpa Gou'er.

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:01.200
Don't worry, everyone.

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.779
Let's wait for Wang Song to come back and see.

00:11:02.919 --> 00:11:04.460
Unity and fraternity.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:06.200
Wang Song.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.919
How's the situation with Uncle Liang?

00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:08.940
The situation...

00:11:09.539 --> 00:11:10.220
It's great.

00:11:10.879 --> 00:11:12.220
About the same as Professor Fan.

00:11:12.620 --> 00:11:14.399
He also laid out a big table full of stuff.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:16.279
Certificates again?

00:11:16.580 --> 00:11:17.259
Photos.

00:11:17.899 --> 00:11:19.500
All of his precious daughter.

